## Typography
- Use monospace fonts for consistent character width
- Align text to character grids
- Maintain consistent spacing
- Implement clear visual hierarchy

## Layout
- Use container queries for component-level responsiveness
- For **@media** breakpoints, use only the custom media variables from `src/styles/custom-media.css`:
  - `--container-sm` (40rem ≈ 640px)
  - `--container-md` (48rem ≈ 768px)
  - `--container-lg` (64rem ≈ 1024px)
  - `--container-xl` (80rem ≈ 1280px)
- Use `var(--measure)` for max-width constraints
- Apply `95cqi` for container-based sizing
- Maintain consistent padding and spacing patterns
- Test responsive designs thoroughly
- Validate typography scales
- Check color contrast ratios

## Best Practices
- Follow accessibility standards (WCAG)
- Implement progressive enhancement
- Monitor performance metrics
- Use semantic HTML elements
- Validate user input
- Handle errors gracefully
- Keep dependencies updated
- Follow semantic versioning
